name: Mailman
description:
Outlook interoperability nodes for Dynamo (1.3 - 2.0) by Hoss Zamani

Mailman will give Dynamo the ability to send emails, send task requests or create contacts using Outlook. Obviously you first need to have Outlook installed on your computer and signed in to your account in Outlook. This package is tested on Outlook 16. However should work with previous versions as well.
